{"tid":976870,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Maths 問題 究竟無理數次方應該點理解❓","createTime":"2019-01-10T17:23:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T22:43:31.000Z","uid":213441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"efacb6ebd20db5d2e818d880625c640cca709ada","tid":976870,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T17:23:13.000Z","msg":"exponent 係整數/份數都好易明嘅 例如a=10^2 就即係a=2 個10 乘埋一齊<br />\na=10^(1/2) 就係要有2 個a 乘埋一齊先係10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁我想問10^pi 可以點理解 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係有pi 咁多個10 相乘？？？ 想像唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c97723ad537b01254264c5dc8b837c62009b20","tid":976870,"uid":1515,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T17:28:02.000Z","msg":"Plot graph會唔會易理解啲<br />\n你咪當10^pi係 in between 10^(314/100)同埋10^(315/100)之間嘅一點"},{"pid":"d829db71bd67316213c6293a78b0630b4f5be738","tid":976870,"uid":44073,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T17:29:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"36dbf3323b2392717005ab2ad3a296bc14a59786","tid":976870,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d829db71bd67316213c6293a78b0630b4f5be738","tid":976870,"uid":44073,"like":2,"dislike":16,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T17:29:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T17:33:41.000Z","msg":"龜蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc88793e13cb3a04dc11f0eb0a12a202d5d3dd07","tid":976870,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T17:34:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb74d855dca5a90c142d71504ebd05147cb55499","tid":976870,"uid":838,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T18:23:22.000Z","msg":"a^b = e^(b * ln a)<br />\n<br />\n淨低嘅問題係點定義e同ln<br />\n<br />\nln可以定義為integrate 1/t from t=1 to t=x<br />\n咁樣ln x就可以有一個簡單易計嘅Taylor series去做數值運算<br />\ne^x可以定義為1+x+x^2/2!+... （同其他定義互通）<br />\n咁就解決到無理數次方嘅問題"},{"pid":"ed140ceaf4853692119d62fee418dbc9af9a83c5","tid":976870,"uid":144406,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T19:00:05.000Z","msg":"Math.pow(10,Math.pi());<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6796aa0ddf25f7064de219580de5e929d1792f09","tid":976870,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T23:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75eca43f57ebc24a436aee4435923ed4cc1c422e","tid":976870,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0863c958793f6a0f4da6815d38080aa1af23bbd2","tid":976870,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:48:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff43fdaa046f1ed434cd6197bcb7ec823f123feb","tid":976870,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb74d855dca5a90c142d71504ebd05147cb55499","tid":976870,"uid":838,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T18:23:22.000Z","msg":"a^b = e^(b * ln a)<br />\n<br />\n淨低嘅問題係點定義e同ln<br />\n<br />\nln可以定義為integrate 1/t from t=1 to t=x<br />\n咁樣ln x就可以有一個簡單易計嘅Taylor series去做數值運算<br />\ne^x可以定義為1+x+x^2/2!+... （同其他定義互通）<br />\n咁就解決到無理數次方嘅問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:52:57.000Z","msg":"照樓主既理解你之後應該要定義埋乜野叫無理數乘以無理數"},{"pid":"bb2bfc86b24579fc156d93a0da78df1804f6e93e","tid":976870,"uid":22302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"Limit"},{"pid":"75c6a37473b4764b0dcc7698cb560ef08dec2055","tid":976870,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"乘法都一樣，乘無理數都係要用limit做"},{"pid":"a6b31ac039188b031040f3fea73635737f6dabe7","tid":976870,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75c6a37473b4764b0dcc7698cb560ef08dec2055","tid":976870,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"乘法都一樣，乘無理數都係要用limit做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b3f9ac2ded58a37b508e09f7b3739868dc4612","tid":976870,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b31ac039188b031040f3fea73635737f6dabe7","tid":976870,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75c6a37473b4764b0dcc7698cb560ef08dec2055","tid":976870,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"乘法都一樣，乘無理數都係要用limit做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:13:49.000Z","msg":"只要知道有理數既乘法係點做，咁你要計a*b for a,b&isin;ℝ\\ℚ既話，咁咪define兩個sequence a_n,b_n converging to a,b, 然後計lim a_n*b_n (個idea大概係咁，嚴重黎講唔知有冇問題，留名等讀數既巴打補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n最簡單又同時最方便實際計算既sequence就係a_n=a既頭n個位<br />\n例如你想乘個&pi;既話就用3, 3.1, 3.14, 3.141, 3.1415, ...<br />\n實際計數上其實你一直都係用緊呢個方法，因為你乘無理數會攞頭個幾個位去乘，然後接受你計出黎個數有好細既error"},{"pid":"f516a4a08c2c54845075dfb94fbca9dfce0435be","tid":976870,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27b3f9ac2ded58a37b508e09f7b3739868dc4612","tid":976870,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b31ac039188b031040f3fea73635737f6dabe7","tid":976870,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75c6a37473b4764b0dcc7698cb560ef08dec2055","tid":976870,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"乘法都一樣，乘無理數都係要用limit做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"講解下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:13:49.000Z","msg":"只要知道有理數既乘法係點做，咁你要計a*b for a,b&isin;ℝ\\ℚ既話，咁咪define兩個sequence a_n,b_n converging to a,b, 然後計lim a_n*b_n (個idea大概係咁，嚴重黎講唔知有冇問題，留名等讀數既巴打補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n最簡單又同時最方便實際計算既sequence就係a_n=a既頭n個位<br />\n例如你想乘個&pi;既話就用3, 3.1, 3.14, 3.141, 3.1415, ...<br />\n實際計數上其實你一直都係用緊呢個方法，因為你乘無理數會攞頭個幾個位去乘，然後接受你計出黎個數有好細既error"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T08:15:48.000Z","msg":"如果a b唔係無限，咁兩個sequence都係bounded，所以個limit係無問題嘅"},{"pid":"5b4a33ab842e36716fb7920b41861adc23ea1adf","tid":976870,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f516a4a08c2c54845075dfb94fbca9dfce0435be","tid":976870,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27b3f9ac2ded58a37b508e09f7b3739868dc4612","tid":976870,"uid":22302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6b31ac039188b031040f3fea73635737f6dabe7","tid":976870,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T07:5